00:32:16.170 --> 00:32:19.050 align:middle line:10%
to determine for
themselves what skill set

00:32:19.050 --> 00:32:20.820 align:middle line:10%
they felt was most necessary.

00:32:20.820 --> 00:32:23.160 align:middle line:10%
Now, the system as
