00:32:23.160 --> 00:32:25.745 align:middle line:10%
who's been in finance, somebody
who's been in government--

00:32:25.745 --> 00:32:27.720 align:middle line:10%
>>LISA: Military.

00:32:27.720 --> 00:32:30.510 align:middle line:84%
>>WILLIAMSON: Whereas they would
