00:33:25.630 --> 00:33:27.630 align:middle line:10%
What makes them less credible?

00:33:27.630 --> 00:33:30.820 align:middle line:84%
Honestly, why would
you be less credible?

00:33:30.820 --> 00:33:31.620 align:middle line:10%
>>LISA: Oh, no.

00:33:31.620 --> 00:33:32.495 align:middle line:10%
>>WILLIAMSON: Really?

00:33:32.495 --> 00:33:34.850 align:middle line:10%
>>LISA: [LAUGHING] The family
