how to run a nation.

00:33:40.190 --> 00:33:40.630 align:middle line:10%
>>LISA: Yes, yes.

00:33:40.630 --> 00:33:42.240 align:middle line:10%
>>WILLIAMSON: And the fact
that we'd been made to feel

00:33:42.240 --> 00:33:43.920 align:middle line:10%
