psychologically inhabit

00:34:25.329 --> 00:34:26.989 align:middle line:90%
the space of that change.

00:34:26.989 --> 00:34:28.530 align:middle line:84%
And now, it's time
for American women

00:34:28.530 --> 00:34:31.679 align:middle line:84%
not just to have certain
