00:34:57.070 --> 00:34:57.870 align:middle line:90%
So you're--

00:34:57.870 --> 00:34:58.810 align:middle line:84%
>>WILLIAMSON: That's my
hope for this campaign.

00:34:58.810 --> 00:35:00.150 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: --a wonderful
representative that way.

00:35:00.150 --> 00:35:01.400 align:middle line:90%
>>WILLIAMSON: Thank you, Lisa.

00:35:01.400 --> 00:35:04.170 align:middle line:10%
