00:35:08.130 --> 00:35:10.800 align:middle line:10%
This is a sea change having
to do with many people seeing

00:35:10.800 --> 00:35:13.380 align:middle line:10%
things differently, knowing
that this is an effort all of us

00:35:13.380 --> 00:35:16.439 align:middle line:10%
